            <abstract>
                <p>Protective prayer against the evil action described as <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">ʾaynat</foreign> ("evil eye") of 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">ṣǝlā</foreign>, which may be an abbreviated form of 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">ṣǝlā wagi</foreign> (literally: "piercer of the shadow"), who was described as a sorcerer or as a 
                    demon by <bibl><ptr target="bm:Worrell1914Zauberwesen"/><citedRange unit="page">136</citedRange></bibl> and 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1972Wellcome"/><citedRange unit="page">52</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
